g Pass: The Inside Story of the New York Jets from the Terrible Titans to Broadway Joe Namath and the Championship of 1968|author=Lou Sahadi|publisher=The World Publishing Company|location=New York|year=1969|ref={{sfnRef|Sahadi}}|isbn=978-1-58567-933-1}} * {{cite book|title=NFL Top 40: The Greatest Pro Football Games Ever Played|author=Sidney Strother|publisher=Viking|location=New York|year=1988|ref={{sfnRef|Strother}}|isbn=978-0-670-82490-8}} * {{cite book|title=The Good, the Bad, and the Ugly Oakland Raiders: Heart-pounding, Jaw-dropping, and Gut-wrenching moments from Oakland Raiders History|author=Steven Travers|publisher=Triumph Books|location=Chicago, Illinois|year=2008|ref={{sfnRef|Travers}}|isbn=978-1-57243-927-6}}
