 the line|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1968/11/16/archives/hot-and-cold-streaks-on-the-line-giants-are-favored-to-extend.html?sq=chargers+bills&scp=10&st=p|newspaper=The New York Times|ref={{sfnRef|''New York Times'', November 16, 1968}}|date=November 16, 1968|accessdate=September 5, 2011|subscription=y}} * {{cite news|title=Oakland jinx hits Jets: Even uniforms are lost|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1968/11/23/archives/oakland-jinx-hits-jets-even-uniforms-are-lost.html?sq=jets+chargers&scp=9&st=p|newspaper=The New York Times|ref={{sfnRef|''New York Times'', November 23, 1968}}|date=November 23, 1968|accessdate=August 20, 2011|subscription=y}} * {{cite journal|title=Great Games: Jets vs. Raiders, 1968|author=Joe Schuster|journal=[[SPORT (magazine)|Sport]]|pages=22–23|ref={{sfnRef|Schuster}}|date=March 1993}} * {{cite news|title=Twenty years later, NBC's ''Heidi'' game remembered|author=Rachel Shuster|newspaper=[[USA Today]]|ref={{sfnRef|Shuster}}|date=November 17, 1988}} * {{cite web |title=Timeline&nbsp;– Raiders Historical Highlights |url=http://www.raiders.com/history/timeline.html |publisher=[[Oakland Raiders]] |accessdate=August 17, 2011 |ref={{sfnRef|Raiders Historical Highlights}} |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/616uLXGJz?url=http://www.raiders.com/history/timeline.html |archivedate=August 21, 2011 |deadurl=yes |df= }} * {{cite news|title=Not like '67: Jets Winging|author=Bob Valli|newspaper=The Oakland Tribune|pages=13–18|ref={{sfnRef|Valli, November 16, 1967}}|date=November 16, 1967}} * {{cite news|title=That clutch Raiders win|author=Bob Valli|newspaper=The Oakland Tribune|pages=33, 39|ref={{sfnRef|Valli, November 18, 1968}}|date=November 18, 1968}} * {{cite news|title=Oakland stops Houston, 40–7|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=96tDAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Aa8MAAAAIBAJ&dq=raiders%20packers%20one%20loss&pg=762%2C25857|agency=[[United Press International]]|newspaper=[[The Altus Times-Democrat]]|via=Google News|page=3|ref={{sfnRef|United Press Internation