{{Infobox company | name = The Society Management | foundation = [[New York City]], New York, [[United States|US]] (2012) | location = [[New York City]], New York, [[United States|US]]
[[:Category:Talent agencies|Talent Agencies]] [[:Category:Modeling agencies|Modeling agencies]] | homepage = [http://www.thesocietymanagement.com www.thesocietymanagement.com] }}
'''The Society Management''' is a model management company based in [[New York City]], [[New York (state)|New York]], and is the official U.S. division of the [[Elite Model Management|Elite World network]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessoffashion.com/2013/04/a-new-model-modelling-agency.html |title=A New Model Modelling Agency |publisher=businessoffashion.com |date= |accessdate=2013-04-12}}</ref> It is also the U.S. branch of the [[Elite Model Look]] contest.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thesocietymanagement.com/a-philosophy.aspx |title=The Society Management, New York |publisher=thesocietymanagement.com |date= |accessdate=2013-04-12}}</ref> The Society Management currently represents [[Adriana Lima]], [[Liu Wen]], [[Erin Wasson]], [[Tao Okamoto]], [[Lindsey Wixson]], [[Sigrid Agren]], [[Kendall Jenner]], [[Grace Jones]], and [[Willow Smith]].<ref name="Models.com">{{cite web|url=http://models.com/agency/The-Society-Management |title=Models.com - The Society Management |publisher=Models.com |date= |accessdate=2013-04-12}}</ref><ref name=thecut>{{cite web|last=Lim|first=James|title=The New Modeling Agency Taking Top New York Models|url=http://nymag.com/thecut/2013/03/lindsey-wixson-joins-new-modeling-agency.html|work=nymag.com/|publisher=New York Magazine|accessdate=20 December 2013|date=20 March 2013}}</ref>
